aboutText: I am rdgr, a 20-year old software engineer who strives to create meaningful and impactful experiences through my work. I have a passion for coding, and I am particularly skilled in TailwindCSS and React, two of the most powerful technologies in web development. My love for technology also extends to my hobbies; I enjoy podcasting and hiking. I believe that the combination of my professional knowledge and my personal interests make me an ideal candidate for a software engineering role. I'm confident that my experience and enthusiasm will be an asset to any team.
